this is actually the subject of ongoing, varied research in terms of
better protections (like Guard selection improvements) to wild
architectures in a datagram world using user space stacks and
optimized dependent link padding across locally classed traffic.

https://blog.torproject.org/category/tags/research
 and
http://freehaven.net/anonbib/
 span the gamut.


> Further, there should be an automatic system to
